State of North Carolina
v.
Silvestre Alvarado Chaves No. 339P16 Supreme Court of North Carolina. December 8, 2016 Mr. Silvestre Alvarado Chaves, For Chaves, Silvestre Alvarado. Mr. Robert C. Montgomery, Special Deputy Attorney General, Mr. Howard S. Boney, Jr., District Attorney, For State of N.C.

ORDER

Ervin, J.

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 12th of September 2016 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Unknown County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 8th of December 2016."
